A. Installation

	A.1	Library install
		$ cd ~/temp/DRIVER_PACKAGE/lib/files/PLATFORM
		$ sudo cp libsdc.so.X.X.X /usr/lib
		$ sudo ldconfig

	A.2	Library uninstall
		$ sudo rm /usr/lib/libsdc.so.X.X.X
		$ sudo ldconfig

	A.3 Sample program
		The library sample program, include source, header and Makefile.

